<p>Reports unresolved channel attributes in <code>@StreamListener</code>, <code>@SendTo</code>, <code>@Output</code>, and <code>@Input</code> annotations.</p>
<p>Using invalid binding name results in 'bean not found' error at runtime.</p>
<p><b>Example:</b></p>
<pre><code lang="java">
  @EnableBinding(Sink.class)
  public class LogSource {
    @StreamListener(Sink.class)
	  public void log1() {
    }

    @StreamListener("invalid")  // Reports 'Cannot find channel'
	  public void log2() {
    }
  }
</code></pre>
